{"tid":1766673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屌狗就話怕比狗拉姐，屌五毛冇問題喇掛？","createTime":"2019-12-02T18:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T16:32:57.000Z","uid":1089,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bd30ed319427bb690976151ac00c38c38433f277","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:50:41.000Z","msg":"鍵盤任務，0成本0風險，唔係咁都唔做呀？<br />\n有線新聞，now新聞, RTHK等中立媒體page長期要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發現好多同路人都係D滿佈自己人既地方屌政府屌到飛天<br />\n可唔可以唔好淨係留喺同溫層例如連登，毒果，立場呢D地方屌，<br />\n要走出去屌先有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上述幾個page正正就係五毛藍屍重災區呀<br />\n目標係要屌走佢地屌到呢班撚樣返去黨人黨地果D地方圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a97c8a2ab635b18c7f63e571ff5a663eeb05cb6","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:53:11.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好睇少五毛呢個問題<br />\n以為無視佢佢地就會收皮？<br />\n忽略呢條戰線既話久而久之佢地講既野就會係呢D地方成為主流<br />\n到時想搶返個場都難"},{"pid":"1d17df8a0bda7183cb6cfeeab0b3f5c3f8f986b4","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n呢個星期睇呢堆中立媒體page唔講以為真係贏撚左"},{"pid":"a8ac439bd38764b868485c58ab3cfca3ff72a7fd","tid":1766673,"uid":303854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"都真<br />\n近排一見到好睇唔順眼就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係以事論事正常討論嘅話 道理係我地呢邊 點都會屌到佢地無野好講<br />\n佢地淨係識講on9廢野擺到明五毛嘅屌兩句就唔好哂時間理佢了 你越理佢佢越開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時同佢地互鬧都幾好笑 可以hea下時間 望住佢地on99柒下柒下講野毫無邏輯個腦好像塞滿屎咁駁唔到好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baf445ca4872f958a68ff4afe5b1e4ef2a1145f","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:03:34.000Z","msg":"唉，懶得屌或者覺得反駁係助長班五毛既話<br />\n留個reaction都好呀，唔係好難姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsocial media玩法一向都係reaction愈多排得愈前<br />\n見到啱聽既留言就幫手推上頂將堆五毛沉底得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f08809b0d28f517025ced05a1cc727e6bb9c8d7","tid":1766673,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:08:56.000Z","msg":"近排幾鍾意睇何志光，佢真係勁鍾意分化，係建制熱狗"},{"pid":"ad47ed68137a239dc3ebf514918d806d5cf66b66","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:16:24.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c435a5efb583daae5eb53845013bddec2ee1daf6","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:20:51.000Z","msg":"補充返，我咁講唔係表示立場毒果既報道有問題<br />\n只係呢兩間太明顯係自己友，留言多數都係同路人<br />\n所以可以既就將火力放係大量五毛藍屍盤踞既page<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81578725b8058d9f4538224cf2f9a4348b8ee673","tid":1766673,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:25:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊組織個鍵盤戰士tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa833fea3b1b2c73563274b881dfe8642965955","tid":1766673,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81578725b8058d9f4538224cf2f9a4348b8ee673","tid":1766673,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:25:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊組織個鍵盤戰士tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:28:18.000Z","msg":"有得諗<br />\n可以針對邊個特定page或者topic要人，重點打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f495acdc628055195d0b5bbe06502637d340fef","tid":1766673,"uid":9640,"l